  <notes>
    The extended metadata schema is LAVERN-inspired but **inline-adopted** (no separate Spaarke ADR — confirmed by spec.md Owner Clarifications table). Cite `lavern-pattern-assessment.md` as inspiration source, not as a Spaarke ADR.

    The 6 global option-sets MUST be created BEFORE the entity columns reference them. Web API EntityDefinitions calls fail with cryptic errors if Choice columns reference unresolved option-set names.

    Do NOT collapse Choice columns into free text. The LLM uses these as discrete signals during meta-tool routing. `Classification = "Deterministic"` is a hard constraint for the `FindResources` semantic search filter, not a hint.

    `IsAlwaysOnInAssistant` and `EvidenceRequired` are stored here but enforced at the dispatch layer in Phase 2. This task only creates the storage shape; runtime enforcement is task 020+.

    Run `dotnet list package --vulnerable --include-transitive` is N/A here (no NuGet additions in a Dataverse-schema task).
  </notes>

